headline: FIS Announces Increase to Quarterly Dividend
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., January 29, 2026--FIS® (NYSE: FIS), a global leader in financial services technology, announced a 10 percent increase to its regular quarterly dividend to $0.44 per common share. The dividend is payable March 24, 2026, to FIS shareholders of record as of close of business on March 10, 2026.
